name: Barnyard Boxes
description:
PDF template for Barnhouse gift boxes to fill with gifts or treats.
These little gift boxes look gorgeous as place settings a ta party or filled with treats or favors.
Each box is 6.5cm wide x 5cm deep x 8cm tall.
The templates come in four different colour ways, are simple to put together and come with full & comprehensive instructions.

1. Make your purchase

2. Within 24 hours (but usually sooner) we will email you your PDF template
